title: FK Raštak
text:
FK Raštak () is a <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> club based in the village of <a href="Ra%C5%A1tak">Raštak</a> near <a href="Skopje">Skopje</a>, <a href="North%20Macedonia">North Macedonia</a>. They currently play in the <a href="Macedonian%20Third%20Football%20League">Macedonian Third League</a> (North Division).
History.
The club was founded in 1959.
